Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.22,0:00:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme a break...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.62,0:00:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have thought that my \NSelf-Destructing Clone would be eaten away too...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.77,0:00:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you my ultimate work of art...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.95,0:00:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Art is explosive!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.05,0:00:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I somehow made it in time...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.00,0:01:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then again, I managed to flee\N{\i1}because that acted as a diversion...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.82,0:01:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My arm's getting sucked into space...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.00,0:01:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What a Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.34,0:01:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What I lost was...\N{\i1}only up to about my elbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.22,0:01:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I must search for my right arm and ring...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.43,0:02:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So this is Sasori's true form, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.31,0:02:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.41,0:02:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Zetsu, here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.42,0:02:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if I can now become\Na member of the Akatsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,One slot has opened up after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.75,0:02:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot... It ain't that easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.66,0:02:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh come on,\Nwhy don't you just let him join...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.84,0:02:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Tobi's a great kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.81,0:03:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.21,0:03:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a sec, Zetsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.73,0:03:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure...\NIt's around here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.61,0:03:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, hey, Zetsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.65,0:03:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, please! Zetsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.31,0:04:59.40,Title,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(695,588)}Return of the Kazekage\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How much longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll be in sight soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Gaara...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.66,0:06:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh...what a lavish welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.13,0:06:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,There are so many people...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as would be expected\Nfor the Kazekage...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.44,0:07:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you're safe...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.19,0:07:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's thanks to everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.65,0:07:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto Uzumaki, I am truly grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.05,0:07:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I...\NI really wasn't able to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.18,0:07:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Kazekage,\Nthe villagers are waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.96,0:07:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Right this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:07:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,First...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.96,0:08:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us pray that\NGranny Chiyo's soul rests in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.43,0:08:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A moment of silent prayer...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.19,0:08:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.96,0:08:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We're home...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.78,0:08:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, are you leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.11,0:08:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You should stay a little longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.23,0:08:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. At least another day...\Nuntil you've rested up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.87,0:08:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to do that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.94,0:09:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I must report to\Nmy Master, the Hokage, immediately...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.13,0:09:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.33,0:09:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And if the Akatsuki have begun\Nto attack villages,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.92,0:09:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel uneasy being away\Nfrom the Leaf Village too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you want to get back\Nas soon as possible, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.10,0:09:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But in that physical condition...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.42,0:09:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to worry...\NI have comrades I can rely on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.05,0:09:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.18,0:09:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, we have already sent\Nthe first report out through Takamaru,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.55,0:09:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's nothing written as to whether the\N two Akatsuki members are dead or alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.87,0:09:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you inform\Nyour village about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.87,0:09:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll report that directly to the Hokage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.83,0:09:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,There are other things\NI'm concerned about too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.98,0:10:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny Chiyo from the Hidden Sand\NVillage is the only casualty,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.17,0:10:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Kazekage has\Nreturned home safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.82,0:10:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Guy's unit and Kakashi's unit\Nhave completed their missions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They anticipate returning to\Nthe Leaf Village in three days' time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.30,0:10:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Lady Tsunade...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.76,0:10:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The last mission went well.\NBut as Master Jiraiya stated...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.55,0:10:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,sending Naruto, a Jinchuriki,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,into a place where there are people\Ntargeting the Tailed Beasts...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.33,0:10:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I question the wisdom of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that former Black Ops Unit\Nmember Kakashi is accompanying him,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,but why take such\Na high risk by sending Naruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:11:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for the very reason that\Nhe's a Jinchuriki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.87,0:11:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The only people who can\Nreally understand Jinchuriki
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.42,0:11:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,are those who are Jinchuriki themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides...that guy has\Na mysterious power...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.26,0:11:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone starts wanting\Nto place their bets on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.89,0:11:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.06,0:11:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny Chiyo's grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,CHIYO
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:12:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she didn't want\Na grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.18,0:12:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought it would\Nbe better to have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.77,0:12:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt that everyone needed\Na place to gather...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.19,0:12:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody, say your farewells...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.32,0:13:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura, Naruto...\NIt's about time to depart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.32,0:13:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Granny Chiyo, thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.66,0:14:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,See you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally I suppose people\Nshake hands and say goodbye...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm not really good with\Nthat kind of stuff, so I'll just leave it at this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei! You guys are too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.97,0:16:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... I'm sorry, Guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.71,0:16:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,When I use that new Sharingan,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.23,0:16:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,it takes a toll on my body\Nfor quite a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.13,0:16:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.39,0:16:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.83,0:17:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.14,0:17:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.32,0:17:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's...kinda disgusting...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Old men giving each other\N{\i1}a piggyback...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's more sickening than I imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh man... That's annoying...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.87,0:17:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! It's training, isn't it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.54,0:17:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Now this way, it'll be faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.63,0:17:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Move, move, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.95,0:17:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys...\NYou think you can keep up with me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.69,0:17:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And when movement gets thrown in,\N{\i1}it's even more sickening.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.42,0:17:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,- Neji...\N- I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like Deidara was done in too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no question that his cause\Nof death is from an explosion...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.54,0:18:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you agree, Zetsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He's probably laying there dead\Nsomewhere around there...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Get your hands off, you jerk...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! He's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to the Jinchuriki?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.78,0:18:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've met my quota...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.57,0:18:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear, oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You barely made it, Deidara...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.66,0:18:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You all right? Guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Tobi, even the patience of\Na saint has limits...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.27,0:18:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Try saying something again and\NI'll decide your cause of death myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.34,0:18:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No doubt it'll be death from explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.15,0:18:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...past the limit...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.18,0:18:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Death from suffocation...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.81,0:19:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already pulled\Nsome strings from behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So that you'll be posted with\NKakashi's squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only are you close in age\Nwith Naruto Uzumaki,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.51,0:19:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but you are also stronger than anyone\Nin the village of the same generation...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And more than anything,\NI admire your superb talent for painting...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.31,0:19:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,From today until the completion\Nof this mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name is...Sai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.74,0:19:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sai. Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.52,0:19:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't put on a fake smile\Nlike that in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.30,0:19:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.79,0:19:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It said in the textbook that in order to charm\N people, you first have to be able to smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.20,0:19:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been practicing, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have difficulty in creating\Nfacial expressions.
